<html>
<head>
<style>body{font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif}</style>
</head>
<body>
    <div id="main">
    <a href="{{siteURL}}"><img src="{{resolve "resource/images/logo.png"}}" alt="OpenMRS ID"></a>
    <h2>Password reset for {{displayName}} ({{username}})</h2>
    <p>The <a href="{{siteURL}}">OpenMRS ID Dashboard</a> received a request to have your OpenMRS ID password reset. To continue with this action, go to the following page:</p>
    <p id="reset-link"><a href="{{resolve urlBase verifyId}}">{{resolve urlBase verifyId}}</a></p>
    <p>This reset email was sent to the following addresses:
    <ul>
        {{#each locals.allEmails}}
            <li>{{this}}</li>
        {{/each}}
    </ul></p>
    <p>If you didn't request a password reset, don't worry.
    This password reset link will deactivate at {{expireDate}}.</p>
    <p>Thanks!</p>
    <p>OpenMRS Community Infrastructure Team</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>